{
  "video_id": "1BS-XUntiLg",
  "title": "Nalini Nadkarni: Life science in prison",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "Trees epitomize stasis."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "Trees are rooted in the ground in one place"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "for many human generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "but if we shift our perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "from the trunk to the twigs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "trees become very dynamic entities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "moving and growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "And I decided to explore this movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "by turning trees into artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "I simply tied the end of a paintbrush onto a twig."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "I waited for the wind to come up and held up a canvas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "and that produced art."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "The piece of art you see on your left"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "is painted by a western red cedar"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "and that on your right by a Douglas fir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "and what I learned was that different species"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "have different signatures, like a Picasso versus a Monet."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "But I was also interested in the movement of trees"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "and how this art might let me capture that and quantify it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "so to measure the distance that a single vine maple tree --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "which produced this painting -- moved in a single year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "I simply measured and summed"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "each of those lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "I multiplied them by the number of twigs per branch"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "and the number of branches per tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "and then divided that by the number of minutes per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "And so I was able to calculate"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "how far a single tree moved in a single year."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "You might have a guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "The answer is actually 186,540 miles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "or seven times around the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "And so simply by shifting our perspective from a single trunk"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "to the many dynamic twigs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "we are able to see that trees are not simply static entities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "but rather extremely dynamic."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "And I began to think about ways that"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "we might consider this lesson of trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "to consider other entities that are also static and stuck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "but which cry for change and dynamicism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "and one of those entities is our prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Prisons, of course, are where people who break our laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "are stuck, confined behind bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "And our prison system itself is stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "The United States has over 2.3 million"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "incarcerated men and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "That number is rising."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "Of the 100 incarcerated people that are released,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "60 will return to prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "Funds for education, for training"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "and for rehabilitation are declining,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "so this despairing cycle of incarceration continues."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "I decided to ask whether the lesson"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "I had learned from trees as artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "could be applied to a static institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "such as our prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "and I think the answer is yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "In the year 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "I started a partnership"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "with the Washington State Department of Corrections."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "Working with four prisons, we began bringing science and scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "sustainability and conservation projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "to four state prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "We give science lectures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "and the men here are choosing to come to our science lectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "instead of watching television or weightlifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "That, I think, is movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "We partnered with the Nature Conservancy"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "for inmates at Stafford Creek Correctional Center"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "to grow endangered prairie plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "for restoration of relic prairie areas in Washington state."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "That, I think, is movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "We worked with the Washington State Department of Fish and Wildlife"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "to grow endangered frogs -- the Oregon spotted frog --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "for later release into protected wetlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "That, I think, is movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "And just recently, we&#39;ve begun to work with"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "those men who are segregated"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "in what we call Supermax facilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve incurred violent infractions"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "by becoming violent with guards"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "and with other prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re kept in bare cells like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "for 23 hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "When they have meetings with their review boards or mental health professionals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re placed in immobile booths like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "For one hour a day"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re brought to these bleak and bland exercise yards."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "Although we can&#39;t bring trees and prairie plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "and frogs into these environments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "we are bringing images of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "into these exercise yards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "putting them on the walls, so at least they get contact"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "with visual images of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "This is Mr. Lopez, who has been in solitary confinement for 18 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s providing input on the types of images"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "that he believes would make him and his fellow inmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "more serene, more calm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "less apt to violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "And so what we see, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "is that small, collective movements of change"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "can perhaps move"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "an entity such as our own prison system"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "in a direction of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "We know that trees are static entities"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "when we look at their trunks."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "But if trees can create art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "if they can encircle the globe seven times in one year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "if prisoners can grow plants and raise frogs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "then perhaps there are other static entities"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "that we hold inside ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "like grief, like addictions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "like racism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "that can also change."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}